Note:
Daily Order of Operations:

1. Flip new season card and resolve, from top to bottom, the actions for that day.

2a. If the season card was a season END card, then go back to #1 and start the next season.

2b. If the season card was a normal season card then it is now the planning phase where you can plan your day with each other (or by yourself).

3. Carry out your actions for the day. You may perform two actions at the  location of your choosing
-OR-                                 
You may perform one action at the location of your choosing and them move to an adjacent location (along the paths) and perform an action at your new location.

4. Return to the farmhouse and select one end of turn action and perform it as many times as you want.

FISH_TRACK_GUIDS = {'c1d82f', '9aa041', 'a7408d', '585516', '513a3c'}
LEGENDARIES_GUIDS = {'8fb808', '64c5cc', '1a6dd2', 'cd33d9'}
FISH_DISCARD_GUID = 'd51b97'

function onLoad()
  fishingZones = {}
  for i, guid in ipairs(FISH_TRACK_GUIDS) do
    local zone = getObjectFromGUID(guid)
    fishingZones[i] = zone
  end

  fishDiscard = getObjectFromGUID(FISH_DISCARD_GUID)
end

function isLegendary(fish)
  for _, guid in ipairs(LEGENDARIES_GUIDS) do
    if fish.guid == guid then
      return true
    end
  end
  return false
end

function fillEmpty()
  for x = 5, 1, -1 do
    if #fishingZones[x].getObjects() == 0 then
      self.takeObject({
        position          = fishingZones[x].getPosition(),
        rotation          = {0,180,0}
      })
    end
  end
end

function findFish()
  local filledZones = {}
  for x = 1, 5 do
    if #fishingZones[x].getObjects() > 0 then
      table.insert(filledZones, x)
    end
  end
  return filledZones
end

function moveFish(fishLocs)
  for x = 1, #fishLocs do
    local fish = fishingZones[fishLocs[x]].getObjects()[1]
    local target = fishingZones[x].getPosition()
    if fishLocs[x] ~= x then
      fish.setPositionSmooth(target)
    end
  end
end

function updateTracker()
  moveFish(findFish())
  Wait.time(function() fillEmpty() end, .5)
end

function fishMigrate()
  local fish1 = fishingZones[1].getObjects()[1]
  local fish2 = fishingZones[2].getObjects()[1]
  if isLegendary(fish1) then
    self.putObject(fish1)
  else
    fishDiscard.putObject(fish1)
  end
  if isLegendary(fish2) then
    self.putObject(fish2)
  else
    fishDiscard.putObject(fish2)
  end
  Wait.time(function() updateTracker() end, .5)
end

SPRING_STANDARD_GUIDS = {'abb5aa', 'ae5883', '5545bf', 'aed97f'}
SPRING_END_GUID = 'e19343'
SPRING_DECK_GUID = '7bedad'

SUMMER_STANDARD_GUIDS = {'428ba8', 'e1d636', '4abc1f', 'd249b7'}
SUMMER_END_GUID = '65f86e'
SUMMER_DECK_GUID  = 'f245d0'

FALL_STANDARD_GUIDS = {'a94b02', 'cae592', 'a91d7c', '888d0f'}
FALL_END_GUID = 'ffac7c'
FALL_DECK_GUID = '9cd89c'

WINTER_STANDARD_GUIDS = {'9f5724', '49ee3a', '4202df', 'e29d62'}
WINTER_END_GUID = 'c0db58'
WINTER_DECK_GUID = 'a2156d'

function onLoad()
  springEnd = getObjectFromGUID(SPRING_END_GUID)
  springDeck = getObjectFromGUID(SPRING_DECK_GUID)

  summerEnd = getObjectFromGUID(SUMMER_END_GUID)
  summerDeck = getObjectFromGUID(SUMMER_DECK_GUID)

  fallEnd = getObjectFromGUID(FALL_END_GUID)
  fallDeck = getObjectFromGUID(FALL_DECK_GUID)

  winterEnd = getObjectFromGUID(WINTER_END_GUID)
  winterDeck = getObjectFromGUID(WINTER_DECK_GUID)
end

function isStandardCard(standardCards, currentCard)
  for _, card in ipairs(standardCards) do
    if currentCard.guid == card then
      return true
    end
  end
  return false
end

function setupYear(params)
  local yPos = self.getPosition().y
  local pos = self.getPosition()
  local standard = params.std

  winterDeck.takeObject({position = {pos.x, yPos, pos.z}, rotation = {0,180,180}, guid = WINTER_END_GUID})
  Wait.time(function() setupSeason(standard, winterDeck, WINTER_STANDARD_GUIDS, {pos.x, yPos+0.5, pos.z}) end, 0.25)

  Wait.time(function() fallDeck.takeObject({position = {pos.x, yPos+1, pos.z}, rotation = {0,180,180}, guid = FALL_END_GUID}) end, .5)
  Wait.time(function() setupSeason(standard, fallDeck, FALL_STANDARD_GUIDS, {pos.x, yPos+1.5, pos.z}) end, .75)

  Wait.time(function() summerDeck.takeObject({position = {pos.x, yPos+2, pos.z}, rotation = {0,180,180}, guid = SUMMER_END_GUID}) end, 1)
  Wait.time(function() setupSeason(standard, summerDeck, SUMMER_STANDARD_GUIDS, {pos.x, yPos+2.5, pos.z}) end, 1.25)

  Wait.time(function() springDeck.takeObject({position = {pos.x, yPos+3, pos.z}, rotation = {0,180,180}, guid = SPRING_END_GUID}) end, 1.5)
  Wait.time(function() setupSeason(standard, springDeck, SPRING_STANDARD_GUIDS, {pos.x, yPos+3.5, pos.z}) end, 1.75)
end

function setupSeason(standard, seasonDeck, standardCards, pos)
  seasonDeck.shuffle()
  if standard then
    for _, card in ipairs(seasonDeck.getObjects()) do
      if isStandardCard(standardCards, card) then
        seasonDeck.takeObject({
          position          = pos,
          rotation          = {0,180,180},
          guid              = card.guid
        })
      end
    end
  else
    for x=1, 4 do
      seasonDeck.takeObject({
        position          = pos,
        rotation          = {0,180,180}
      })
    end
  end
end

function onLoad()
  craftsDeck = getObjectFromGUID(CRAFTS_ROOM_DECK_GUID)
  craftsZone = getObjectFromGUID(CRAFTS_ROOM_ZONE_GUID)

  pantryDeck = getObjectFromGUID(PANTRY_DECK_GUID)
  pantryZone = getObjectFromGUID(PANTRY_ZONE_GUID)

  tankDeck = getObjectFromGUID(FISH_TANK_DECK_GUID)
  tankZone = getObjectFromGUID(FISH_TANK_ZONE_GUID)

  bullDeck = getObjectFromGUID(BULL_BOARD_DECK_GUID)
  bullZone = getObjectFromGUID(BULL_BOARD_ZONE_GUID)

  vaultDeck = getObjectFromGUID(VAULT_DECK_GUID)
  vaultZone = getObjectFromGUID(VAULT_ZONE_GUID)

  boilDeck = getObjectFromGUID(BOIL_ROOM_DECK_GUID)
  boilZone = getObjectFromGUID(BOIL_ROOM_ZONE_GUID)
end

function fillCommCenter()
  drawBundle(craftsDeck, craftsZone)
  Wait.time(function() drawBundle(pantryDeck, pantryZone) end, .5)
  Wait.time(function() drawBundle(tankDeck, tankZone) end, 1)
  Wait.time(function() drawBundle(bullDeck, bullZone) end, 1.5)
  Wait.time(function() drawBundle(vaultDeck, vaultZone) end, 2)
  Wait.time(function() drawBundle(boilDeck, boilZone) end, 2.5)
end

function drawBundle(deck, zone)
  deck.shuffle()
  deck.takeObject({
    position          = zone.getPosition(),
    rotation          = {0,180,180}
  })
end

STARTING_PARSNIP_GUID = 'd9eaf8'
FARM_ZONE_GUIDS = {'45e65a', '89d53e', '39b434', 'f8cb12', '9a71c7'}
FARM_BUILDING_ZONES_GUIDS = {'04195d', '262328'}
FARM_BUILDING_BAG_GUID = 'bd2b48'
WATERED_CROP_ZONE_GUID = 'cadbb1'

function onLoad()
  farmZones = {}
  for _, plot in ipairs(FARM_ZONE_GUIDS) do
    local farm = getObjectFromGUID(plot)
    table.insert(farmZones, farm)
  end

  farmBuildingZones = {}
  for _, build in ipairs(FARM_BUILDING_ZONES_GUIDS) do
    local buildZone = getObjectFromGUID(build)
    table.insert(farmBuildingZones, buildZone)
  end

  farmBuildingBag = getObjectFromGUID(FARM_BUILDING_BAG_GUID)
  startingParsnip = getObjectFromGUID(STARTING_PARSNIP_GUID)
  wateredZone = getObjectFromGUID(WATERED_CROP_ZONE_GUID)
end

function getStartingParsnip()
  startingParsnip.setRotation({0,180,0})
  startingParsnip.setPositionSmooth(farmZones[2].getPosition())
end

function randomizeBuildOptions()
  for x, zone in ipairs(farmBuildingZones) do
    Wait.time(function()
      if #zone.getObjects() == 0 then
        farmBuildingBag.takeObject({
          position          = zone.getPosition(),
          rotation          = {0, 180, 180}
        })
      end
    end, .25*x)
  end
end

function waterAllCrops()
  for x, zone in ipairs(farmZones) do
    if #zone.getObjects() > 0 then
      waterCrop(x)
    end
  end
end

function waterCrop(index)
  local crops = farmZones[index].getObjects()
  if index > 1 then
    for x, _ in ipairs(crops) do
      crops[x].setPositionSmooth(farmZones[index-1].getPosition())
    end
  else
    for x, _ in ipairs(crops) do
      farmZones[index].getObjects()[x].setPositionSmooth(wateredZone.getPosition())
    end
    print('A crop is ready to be gathered from the Farm')
  end
end

SPRING_BAG_GUID = 'a02c02'
SPRING_TREE_TILE_GUIDS = {'4f9274', '7bb9e6', 'e7569e', 'a6d9f1'}

SUMMER_BAG_GUID = '37bf21'
SUMMER_TREE_TILE_GUIDS = {'42e4b0', '55e0aa', '2623e2', '7446c1'}

FALL_BAG_GUID = '08ce75'
FALL_TREE_TILE_GUIDS = {'e0a0a9', '2fff00', '30e3cb', '427908'}

WINTER_BAG_GUID = '18ceb2'
WINTER_TREE_TILE_GUIDS = {'5f93f9', '488c20', '9d3231', '5fe891'}

TREE_SPOTS_GUIDS = {'b97908', 'a6cd50', 'b749b9', '970d0a'}
FORAGE_SPOTS_GUIDS = {'0ef341', 'be7b21', '172c28', 'b58a53', '588e17', 'b319dc', 'fda826', '247a08', '97284d', '414deb', 'd17caf'}

function onLoad()
  currentSeason = 0
  springForage = getObjectFromGUID(SPRING_BAG_GUID)
  summerForage = getObjectFromGUID(SUMMER_BAG_GUID)
  fallForage = getObjectFromGUID(FALL_BAG_GUID)
  winterForage = getObjectFromGUID(WINTER_BAG_GUID)

  treeZones = {}
  for _, tree in ipairs(TREE_SPOTS_GUIDS) do
    local zone = getObjectFromGUID(tree)
    table.insert(treeZones, zone)
  end

  forageZones = {}
  for _, forage in ipairs(FORAGE_SPOTS_GUIDS) do
    local zone = getObjectFromGUID(forage)
    table.insert(forageZones, zone)
  end
end

function clearForageZones(sBag)
  for _, zone in ipairs(forageZones) do
    if #zone.getObjects() > 0 then
      for _, obj in ipairs(zone.getObjects()) do
        sBag.putObject(obj)
      end
    end
  end
  for _, zone in ipairs(treeZones) do
    if #zone.getObjects() > 0 then
      for _, obj in ipairs(zone.getObjects()) do
        sBag.putObject(obj)
      end
    end
  end
  return true
end

function setupTiles(tGuids, sBag)
  for x, zone in ipairs(treeZones) do
    if #zone.getObjects() == 0 then
      sBag.takeObject({
        position          = zone.getPosition(),
        rotation          = {0,180,180},
        guid              = tGuids[x]
      })
    end
  end
  for _, zone in ipairs(forageZones) do
    if #zone.getObjects() == 0 then
      sBag.takeObject({
        position          = zone.getPosition(),
        rotation          = {0,180,180}
      })
    end
  end
end

function setupNextSeason()
  if currentSeason == 0 then
    setupTiles(SPRING_TREE_TILE_GUIDS, springForage)
  elseif currentSeason == 1 then
    clearForageZones(springForage)
    Wait.time(function() setupTiles(SUMMER_TREE_TILE_GUIDS, summerForage) end, .5)
  elseif currentSeason == 2 then
    clearForageZones(summerForage)
    Wait.time(function() setupTiles(FALL_TREE_TILE_GUIDS, fallForage) end, .5)
  elseif currentSeason == 3 then
    clearForageZones(fallForage)
    Wait.time(function() setupTiles(WINTER_TREE_TILE_GUIDS, winterForage) end, .5)
  else
    print('Final Season Reached!')
  end
  currentSeason = currentSeason + 1
end

BOTTOM_LEVEL_GUID = '38f04d'
MINE_MAP_DECK_GUID = 'a20cfa'

function onLoad()
  mineMapDeck = getObjectFromGUID(MINE_MAP_DECK_GUID)
end

function nextLevel()
  local deck = self.getObjects()[1]
  local cards = deck.getObjects()
  local moveCard = cards[#cards]
  local deckPos = deck.getPosition()
  if moveCard.guid ~= BOTTOM_LEVEL_GUID then
    deck.setPosition({deckPos.x, deckPos.y + .2 ,deckPos.z})
    deck.takeObject({
      position          = self.getPosition(),
      rotation          = {0, 90, 0},
      guid              = moveCard.guid,
      smooth            = false
    })
  end
  mineMapDeck.call('pullNewMap')
end

function onLoad()
  oneCoinBag = getObjectFromGUID(ONE_COIN_BAG_GUID)
  fiveCoinBag = getObjectFromGUID(FIVE_COIN_BAG_GUID)
  tenCoinBag = getObjectFromGUID(TEN_COIN_BAG_GUID)
  moneyBowl = getObjectFromGUID(MONEY_BOWL_GUID)
  dropP = {x = self.getPosition().x - 1, y = self.getPosition().y + 1, z = self.getPosition().z}
end

function counting()
  local numObjects = #self.getObjects()
  total = 0
  while true do
    if numObjects ~= #self.getObjects() then
      numObjects = #self.getObjects()
      total = 0
      total = total + countSingles().amt + countFives().amt + countTens().amt
      moneyBowl.setName(total)
    end
  end
end

function startingCoins()
  for x = 1, 3, 1 do
    Wait.frames(function()
      oneCoinBag.takeObject({
        position          = {dropP.x + 0.5 * x, dropP.y, dropP.z},
        rotation          = {45, 180, 45}
      })
    end, 15*x)
  end
end

function updateCoinBowl()
  local onesCnt = countSingles()
  local fivesCnt = 0
  Wait.frames(function() exchangeSingles(onesCnt) end, 15)
end

function countSingles()
  local cnt = 0
  local oneCoins = {}
  for _, coin in ipairs(self.getObjects()) do
    if coin.hasTag('coin_1') then
      cnt = cnt+1
      table.insert(oneCoins, coin)
    end
  end
  return {cnt = count, amt = count}
end

function countFives()
  local count = 0
  for _, coin in ipairs(self.getObjects()) do
    if coin.hasTag('coin_5') then
      count = count+1
    end
  end
  return {cnt = count, amt = count*5}
end

function countTens()
  local count = 0
  for _, coin in ipairs(self.getObjects()) do
    if coin.hasTag('coin_10') then
      count = count+1
    end
  end
  return {cnt = count, amt = count*10}
end

function exchangeSingles(singles)
  local loop = singles.count - remainder(singles.count, 5)
  local bowl = self.getObjects()
  local coins = singles.coins
  while loop > 0 do
    oneCoinBag.putObject(coins[loop])
    loop = loop - 1
  end
  --[[
  if cnt > 0 then
    Wait.frames(function()
      local fives = cnt / 5
      for x = 1, fives, 1 do
        fiveCoinBag.takeObject({
          position          = {dropP.x + 0.5 * x, dropP.y, dropP.z},
          rotation          = {45, 180, 45}
        })
      end
    end, 15*x)
  end
  ]]
end

function exchangeFives(cnt)
  cnt = cnt - remainder(cnt, 2)
  for x = 1, cnt, 1 do
    for _, coin in ipairs(self.getObjects()) do
      if coin.hasTag('coin_5') then
        oneCoinBag.putObject(coin)
        break
      end
    end
  end
  if cnt > 0 then
    Wait.frames(function()
      local fives = cnt / 2
      for x = 1, fives, 1 do
        tenCoinBag.takeObject({
          position          = {dropP.x + 0.5 * x, dropP.y, dropP.z},
          rotation          = {45, 180, 45}
        })
      end
    end, 15*x)
  end
end

function remainder(x,y)
  while x >= y do
    x = x - y
  end
  return x
end
